data.text:
To be featured in the 2025 Dome Yearbook, sign up for your senior portrait at this link: https://laurenorders.com/login

Enter your client ID, which is 25DOME-YOURNDID, then follow the prompts to schedule your appointment. Appointments will be availble throughout the fall semester.

Portraits are being taken on the second floor of Duncan Student Center behind the radio stations.
